node.text:
The 'Comune di Roma Capitale'.
Located in Rome, Italy.
Video by Kirill Neiezhmakov (@neiezhmakov).
.
"It is better to imitate ancient than modern work." — Leonardo da Vinci. #architectureoskar
.
#roma #rome #italy #leonardodavinci

node.text:
Modern forest house 💚 #archoskar
The 'Open Valley House' (256 m²).
Designed by ravstudiomx (@ravstudiomx, 2017).
Located in Tapalpa, Jalisco, México.
Photos by César Béjar (@cesarbejarstudio).
.
"Each new situation requires a new architecture." — Jean Nouvel. #architectureoskar
.
#modern #forest #architecture #mexico

node.text:
Palm observation deck 🌴 #archoskar
The 'View at The Palm' (@theviewpalm).
Designed by Gensler.
Located in Dubai, UAE.
Video by Yousef Alkaabi (@yousef_alkaabi).
Song by Gustavo Bravetti, 'Babel'.
.
"You can design and create, and build the most wonderful place in the world. But it takes people to make the dream a reality." — Walt Disney. #architectureoskar
.
#palm #dubai #deck #disney

node.text:
Bali beach house 🤍 #archoskar
The 'Retreat' (200 m²).
Designed by My Shrine (@myshrine_designs).
Located in Pererenan Beach, Bali, Indonesia.
Photos by Sheila Man (@sheilaman_, @baliinteriors).
.
"Never be in a hurry; do everything quietly and in a calm spirit. Do not lose your inner peace for anything whatsoever, even if your whole world seems upset." — Saint Francis de Sales. #architectureoskar
.
#bali #beach #retreat #indonesia

node.text:
Mountainside ride 💦 #archoskar
The 'Parque de Atracciones Monte Igueldo' ('Mount Igueldo Amusement Park').
Located in Donostia-San Sebastian, Spain.
Video Beatriz Alemán (@beaa.alem).
Song by The Macarons Project, 'Moon River'.
Description by Monte Igueldo.
.
"You cannot step into the same river twice." — Heraclitus. #architectureoskar
.
Inaugurated in 1911, Monte Igueldo has slowly but unstoppably morphed into the attraction that everyone knows in Donostia, combining tradition and modernity, the original attractions coexist with new ones. Monte Igueldo is an emblematic place for the people of San Sebastian and an unforgettable experience for the ones visiting it for the first time.
.
#mountain #rollercoaster #river #spain

node.text:
Greek boutique hotel ✨ #archoskar
The 'OLEA ALL SUITE HOTEL'.
Designed by Block722 architects+ (@block722architects, 2018).
Located in Zakynthos, Greece.
Photos by Guilherme Silva da Rosa (@darosa.cc).
Description by Block722 architects+.
.
"Quality is not an act, it is a habit." — Aristotle. #architectureoskar
.
'OLEA ALL SUITE HOTEL' is situated on the island of Zakynthos. Perched organically on an evergreen hill in Tsilivi, sheltered from the winds and merging with the emerald colors of the lush natural landscape, the Olea All Suite Hotel is a contemporary, peaceful retreat; a design-led sanctuary that taps into the ever-present element of water.
.
#greek #boutique #zakynthos #greece

node.text:
Bright and curved residence ✨ #archoskar
The 'Curvature' (500 m²).
Designed by OFFICE 313 (@office_313, 2021).
Located in Kuwait City, Kuwait.
Photos by Mohammad Taqi Ashkanani (@mashkanani).
Description by OFFICE 313.
.
"Evolution is a light illuminating all facts, a curve that all lines must follow." — Pierre Teilhard de Chardin. #architectureoskar
.
The essence of this project lies behind the interplay of extremes that exist within. OFFICE 313’S strategy was to design a space that immerses its visitors in an environment that hosts an interplay of light and dark. By linking the indoor to the outdoor, regulates the climate as well as provides the guests with a harmonious living space.
.
#bright #curve #light #dark

node.text:
Contemporary dark penthouse 🖤 #archoskar
The 'Vancouver House Penthouse' (334 m²).
Designed by Leckie Studio (@leckiestudio).
Located in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada.
Photos by Conrad Brown (@conradbrownphoto).
Description by Leckie Studio.
.
"Art is a harmony parallel with nature." — Paul Cezanne. #architectureoskar
.
This two-bedroom penthouse in the new Vancouver House tower was conceived as a warm space for living, socializing, and displaying the client’s collection of art and natural artifacts. Positioned on the tower’s northwest side, the two-story unit features expansive views of English Bay and the North Shore Mountains, which the designers hoped to weave into a layered and balanced environment that looked both inward and outward.
.
#contemporary #dark #penthouse #vancouver
